This paper is primarily focused on image captioning, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL) sub-categories. The paper also discusses different model architectures, training objectives, hyperparameter settings, and decoding procedures, which are all related to machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI) and information retrieval (cs.IR).
